title: Hour 1 - Cris Collinsworth (05-21-20)

description:
Cris Collinsworth is not a betting man but he does pay attention to the odds for NFL teams to be successful. Cris talks to Dan about the NFL being a copy cat league especially at wide receiver with the passing game.
